cql:
library BonnieTestBasic2 version '0.0.001'

using QDM version '5.3'

valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1'
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'
valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837'
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'
valueset "Laboratory Tests for Hypertension": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.600.1482'
valueset "Patient Reason refused": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.600.791'
valueset "Beta Blocker Therapy for LVSD": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1184'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
	["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
	["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
	["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
	["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Denominator":
	exists ["Medication, Not Ordered": "Beta Blocker Therapy for LVSD"] NoBetaBlocker
		where NoBetaBlocker.negationRationale in "Patient Reason refused"

define "Initial Assessments":
	["Assessment, Performed": "Laboratory Tests for Hypertension"] A
		where A.result as DateTime during "Measurement Period"

define "Foo":
	["Laboratory Test, Performed": "Laboratory Tests for Hypertension"] Test
		with "Initial Assessments" Assessment
			such that exists ( Test.components Comp
					where Assessment.result as DateTime < Comp.result as DateTime
			)

define "Initial Population":
	exists "Initial Assessments"

define "Numerator":
	exists "Foo"
title: Bonnie Test Basic 2
